      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……次は芽衣のセリフだな\n「いつもここで猫ちゃん撫でてるよね」",
      "startTime": 5.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "「芽衣もここ、よく来るんだ～\n羨ましいなって思って見てたんだよ」",
      "startTime": 11.4284347082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "「その大きな手でなでなでされたいなって……\nねぇ、芽衣のこと君だけの猫ちゃんにしてほしいな」",
      "startTime": 19.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ～、{user}さんの音読でも\nこれだけグッとくるんですね～！",
      "startTime": 27.6634863207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "きっと芽衣ちゃんが言ったら\n会場のみんな、めろめろになっちゃいますよ～！",
      "startTime": 32.7248551277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "君だけの猫ちゃん、っていうのはよく分からないが……\n良かったよ。い、今ので終わりだったよな？",
      "startTime": 40.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、すずちゃんのセリフが残ってますよ\nもうちょっとですから！　お願いします！",
      "startTime": 47.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ない……行くぞ！　「やっと見つけましたわ！\nもう！　ちゃんと私、教室でって言いましたわよね！」",
      "startTime": 55.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "「え？　私とあなた、どっちの教室でかは聞いてない？\nつ、伝え忘れたかもしれませんわね、ごめんなさい」",
      "startTime": 67.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "「こんな時でも怒らず、いつも優しく付き合ってくれて\n感謝していますのよ……だから……」",
      "startTime": 76.8999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\nそこで腕を組んで胸を張って！",
      "startTime": 81.7999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "「私からのチョコを受け取る権利を差し上げますわ！\n……好き、ですのよ。あなたのこと」",
      "startTime": 88.7999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、今の凄く良かったです！\n今日一番の迫真の演技でしたよ！",
      "startTime": 97.1666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "渚の演技指導のおかげで、レベルアップしたのかもな\nこれで告白企画は大丈夫そうか？",
      "startTime": 104.4333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　{user}さんのおかげです\nところで、私の告白はどうでしたか……？",
      "startTime": 110.6935790552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "きっと私、君のことが、好き……好きなの\n離れちゃう前から、ずっとずっと……好きなの",
      "startTime": 125.2666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "シチュエーション告白、いろいろやってはみたものの\nやっぱり本人に寄せる方がいいのかな……って悩んでて",
      "startTime": 136.9333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだなぁ……やっぱり、渚らしいのが一番だと思うよ\nいや、渚の告白はどれも凄く良かったけどな",
      "startTime": 147.3000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　良かったですか！？\nぎゅんっってきましたか？",
      "startTime": 153.5666641236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "「きゅん」じゃなくて「ぎゅん」、か！？\nさ、さすがに、それは分からないが",
      "startTime": 158.7333307903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、変なこと聞いちゃってごめんなさい\n……でも、良かった",
      "startTime": 166.8284478263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "これでセンターとしても、月ストの一員としても\n出来ることがまた一つ増えました",
      "startTime": 173.2666641236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "センターの、歌やパフォーマンスの輝きだけじゃなく\nファンのために企画まで考えて……凄いな、渚は",
      "startTime": 179.8333307903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そうですよ～。一杯、頑張ってるんですから\n琴乃ちゃんにお願いして、頭撫でてもらいたいくらい",
      "startTime": 190.7999974569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげで\n胸キュンセリフもだいぶ固まってきましたし",
      "startTime": 196.5999974569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ当日は、ファンのみんなをぎゅんっと\nさせちゃいますから、楽しみにしてて下さいね！",
      "startTime": 202.6666671754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ぎゅんっ！　っとさせてくれ\nでもその前に、まずは新曲のMV撮影だな",
      "startTime": 209.6666671754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "今日の渚の表情や雰囲気\nきっと曲にピッタリだと思ったよ",
      "startTime": 216.6000127157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえると、ますます自信持っちゃいます\nまずはMV撮影で今日の成果を発揮しちゃいますよ～！",
      "startTime": 223.1666793824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "startTime": 229.2144795581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……ここで五人順番にバストアップで……\nその前がダンスで全身を、この並びで……",
      "startTime": 235.9666793824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "渚、そろそろ撮影が始まるから行こう\nあれだけ練習してきたんだ、大丈夫だよ",
      "startTime": 243.6000127157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、もう時間ですね……すーーはーー……\nうん、大丈夫……行きましょう！",
      "startTime": 255.394769501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_13_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（そろそろ本番だな……渚の様子は……）\n（さっきまでワタワタしてたけど、もう大丈夫そうだな）",
